Open source as weapon
 
 
 
 
 
 
I often talk about the use of an open play as weapon, a mechanism of changing the environment you exist in. Back in 2011, when I examined the phenotypic changes of companies (due to a particular cycle known as peace, war and wonder -  more details here ) there was a pronounced change in attitude in the next gen